revision.text:
This is a code snippet from Jelpi (by zep) that can be used in any game to oft hilarious effect.
for i=1,5 do poke(rnd(0x8000),rnd(0x100)) end Here is an alternate corruptor, using a different method. function _init() a=1 b=1 c=1 end function _update() b=peek(a) a=a+c poke(a,b)
if a < 0 then a = 1 end a=a+1 srand(c) c=flr(rnd(30)) end

